<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215494>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Domorganus suecicus sp. n., holotype female (A – E, H – I) and paratype male (F – G). A: Anterior end, median section; B: Anterior end, surface view; C: Pharyngeal region; D: Renette cell and coelomocytes; E: Female tail, F: Male tail, G: Male cloacal region; H: Entire female; I: Anterior part of the female reproductive system. Scale bar: A – B, G = 10 µm; C – F, I = 20 µm, H = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

